tion: D 388–38, according to the standards established in the American Society for Testing Materials on Coal and Coke under standard specifications for Classification of Coals by Rank, contained in public-land deposits considered as valuable under the coal-land classification standards established by the Secretary of the Interior and prescribed in section 30, Code of Federal Regulations, part 201; and “source material” shall mean uranium, thorium, or any other material which is determined by the Atomic Energy Commission pursuant to the provisions of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2091"},"text":"section 2091 of title 42","children":[],"tail":" to be source material."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id60069bd7-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1955-08-11/ch795/s6"},"text":"Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 795, § 6","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/69/680"},"text":"69 Stat. 680","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id60069bd8-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id60069bd9-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id60069bda-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Act of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1914-10-20"},"text":"October 20, 1914","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, is "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1914-10-20/ch330"},"text":"act Oct. 20, 1914, ch. 330","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href"